        "body": "This PR addresses the issue of missing Hindi translations where several UI elements were displaying in English when the Hindi locale was selected. It ensures a complete localized experience for Hindi users.\r\n\r\n## Changes\r\n- Added 40+ missing translation keys to [src/i18n/locales/hi.js](cci:7://file:///Users/aditi/drawdb/src/i18n/locales/hi.js:0:0-0:0).\r\n- Included translations for terms like \"Export saved data\", \"Clear cache\", \"Show datatype\", \"Snap to grid\", and more.\r\n\r\n## Related Issue\r\nFixes #[Issue Number]\r\n",
